#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:595
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If &ktimetracker; is configured to log history, it will record every start/"
"stop timer event. This history is not cleared when times are reset and "
"remains on file until the task is deleted."
msgstr ""
"Kui &ktimetracker;ile on antud korraldus ajalugu logida, salvestab rakendust "
"kõigi taimerite iga käivitamise ja peatamise. Seda ajalugu ei puhastata ka "
"aja nullimisel ning see püsib alal seni, kuni sa vastava faili füüsiliselt "
"hävitad."

